Now that you know what works:

- Maintain 60% of budget on proven concepts (refresh with new faces).
- Test 30% on new angles/hooks.
- Reserve 10% for seasonal/trending opportunities.

Introduce creator tiers:

- **Tier 1 (your MVPs):** 3-4 creators who nail your brand every time—pay retainer.
- **Tier 2 (solid performers):** 5-8 creators for volume and variety.
- **Tier 3 (testing pool):** New creators auditioning for ongoing work.

**Budget allocation:** ₹80,000-₹100,000.

### Month 3 (Optimization): 30-40 Creatives

You now have a UGC machine:

- 70% proven concepts (winning angles with fresh creators).
- 20% new experiments.
- 10% AI-enhanced variations.

Build your content reserves:

- Always have 10-15 "ready-to-launch" creatives in reserve.
